Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveCrooner, Tiwa Savage’s former husband, Tunju Ibrahim Balogun, better known as Teebillz, has welcomed a son with another woman.
Tiwa Savage and Teebillz walked down the aisle in 2013 and went their separate ways in 2018.
The duo have a son named, Jamil.
Teebillz took to his verified Instagram page to announced the arrival of his child with his American based lover.
According to him, it’s the most amazing feeling ever.
“Blessed to experience the most amazing feeling once again…….King Zayn” He tagged the photo.

Nigerian celebrities, fans and followers of the music executive have taken to his Instagram comment section to congratulate him.
Recalls that Teebillz once left tongues wagging online after he declared Tacha the most bankable without opening her legs among other BBN housemates.
Teebillz, who had on several occasions sing the praises of the reality TV star even after the termination of the management deal between them, has once again proved that Tacha is making waves through legitimate means.
His post attracted reactions from other female BBNaija ex-housemates, including Nina.
